<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="59" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,153,431]" pageId="14" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,369,395]" pageId="14" pageNumber="59">Remarks.</emphasis>
As is the case with the nocturnal and aposematic distasteful adult 
<taxonomicName box="[1063,1201,369,395]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="59" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Lampyridae</taxonomicName>
